Package: a4syahpradana
Title: Exploring The Most Common Name in America
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Akbar Rakha", "Syahpradana", , "asya0008@student.monash.edu",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package provides a cleaned dataset of the most common
    first and last name combinations in America, including baseline
    and adjusted estimates. It also includes helper functions to
    summarise and rank names for visualisation and exploration.
